snippet.title: Punch Kick Duck - Out Now on iOS and Android!
snippet.description:
Just when you least expected it... a new release from Pipsqueak Games! Get ready to PUNCH KICK DUCK. Out now on iOS and coming soon to Android!
- Available now on the App Store: ► https://apps.apple.com/us/app/punch-kick-duck/id1623039444
- Get it on Google Play: ► https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.pipsqueakgames.pkd

From the creator of SHOOT THE MOON , PUNCH KICK DUCK is a compact, lovingly made score-chaser fighting game for mobile, designed to challenge your skill without emptying your wallet.
https://punchkickduck.com
